nominated, and eventually won,

00:34:06.620 --> 00:34:09.660
but he should get to Philadelphia.

00:34:09.660 --> 00:34:14.020
Since Roosevelt was such a shoe-in
at the Democratic Convention,

00:34:16.460 --> 00:34:21.070
