fighter, they were both Jewish,

00:34:53.650 --> 00:34:56.730
they got in the ring, and
they couldn't hit each other,

00:34:56.730 --> 00:35:01.290
they just couldn't do it, so there
were 4,000 people in the arena

00:35:01.290 --> 00:35:04.370
and by the second round, there were
2,000 people, by the third round,

00:35:04.370 --> 00:35:08.520
